data.description: Incredibly well maintained home.  Four Bedrooms and two baths with comfortable floor plan.  Kitchen with newer appliances (Refrig does not convey).  Wood look tile is beautiful and easy to care for.  Family room is large and opens out to gorgeous pool area.  Two fireplaces to enjoy on those cool nights.  Yard is low maintenance, with artificial grass in back/side and easy care rocks in front yard.  Two car garage.  Must see to appreciate how well maintained this home is....move right in.  OPEN House Sat. 10/7 12-3
